    <details>
      <summary>üéñÔ∏è Off the Court</summary>
      <p>
        LeBron is known for his philanthropy, notably founding the "I PROMISE School" in Akron to help underprivileged students.
        He is also active in media, producing films and documentaries through his company, SpringHill Entertainment.
      </p>
    </details>
